---
import Calendly from '../components/Calendly.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import '../styles/global.css'
---

<Layout>
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="py-16 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-3xl leading-tight font-bold text-[#1D3557]">
				Clear Next Steps for Your Planning Center Strategy
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-xl text-[#333333]">
				...so you can get back to what matters most: <span class="font-bold">ministry</span>.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-6 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				Feeling stuck or overwhelmed by the tech side of things? Let's make Planning Center work for
				you, not against you.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-12">
				<Calendly />
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<!-- Problem Section -->
	<div class="container mx-auto bg-[#F5F5F5] px-4 py-12">
		<section class="px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
					Planning Center shouldn't feel like a second full-time job.
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-6 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
					You signed up for Planning Center to help you lead more efficiently—not to spend hours
					googling how to make it all work. But between endless how-to videos, a tangled database,
					and too many volunteers slipping through the cracks, it's easy to feel stuck, overwhelmed,
					and like ministry is taking a back seat to admin work.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-6 text-lg font-medium text-[#333333] italic">
					You shouldn't need a tech degree to do what God called you to do.
				</p>
				<ul class="mx-auto max-w-md space-y-3 text-left text-[#333333]">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 text-[#A8C686]">✔</span>
						Anxious about missing people or follow-ups
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 text-[#A8C686]">✔</span>
						Unsure if you're even using PCO “right”
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 text-[#A8C686]">✔</span>
						Wasting hours on tasks that should be automatic
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 text-[#A8C686]">✔</span>
						Volunteers slipping away unnoticed
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<section class="bg-[#F5F5F5] px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
			<!-- Empathy -->
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
				I get it—ministry isn't supposed to feel like managing a startup.
			</h2>
			<p class="mb-10 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				When I started in ministry, I was fired up to connect with people and share the message of
				Jesus. But the admin side quickly became overwhelming. Planning Center had potential, but it
				felt like learning a new language.
				<br class="hidden sm:block" />
				After years of trial and error, I finally learned how to make it work <strong>for</strong> me—not
				against me. Now I help churches do the same, saving hours of time and helping pastors get back
				to what they were actually called to do.
			</p>

			<!-- Authority -->
			<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">
				I've spent the late nights, so you don't have to.
			</h3>
			<p class="text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				I've worked with churches of all sizes to streamline their Planning Center setups—from
				Sunday check-ins to automated follow-ups—so leaders can spend more time shepherding people
				and less time chasing systems. Whether you're just getting started or rebuilding after
				losing a key team member, I'll help you get clarity, fast.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Plan -->
	<section class="bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
				A simple process to turn chaos into clarity
			</h2>
			<p class="mb-10 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				You don't need to overhaul everything to get results. This streamlined process gives you
				clear wins, fast—without taking over your week.
			</p>

			<div class="space-y-6 text-left">
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<!-- Number 1 with underline -->
					<div
						class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] underline decoration-[#A8C686] decoration-4"
					>
						1
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333]">Book your Health Check</p>
						<p class="text-[#333333]">
							We'll have a quick chat about your current setup and what you're hoping to improve.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<!-- Number 2 with underline -->
					<div
						class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] underline decoration-[#A8C686] decoration-4"
					>
						2
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333]">Get a customized audit</p>
						<p class="text-[#333333]">
							On our Zoom call, I'll walk you through your Planning Center setup, highlight areas to
							optimize, and offer 1–3 quick wins on the spot.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<!-- Number 3 with underline -->
					<div
						class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] underline decoration-[#A8C686] decoration-4"
					>
						3
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333]">Walk away with a blueprint</p>
						<p class="text-[#333333]">
							You'll receive a full report, a Loom walkthrough, and a plan to move forward—DIY or
							done-for-you.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="mt-10 text-base text-[#333333] italic sm:text-lg">
				Whether you just need direction or want someone to handle it for you, you'll walk away with
				clarity and momentum.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Success Section -->
	<section class="bg-[#A8C686] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
				More time for ministry. Less time managing systems.
			</h2>
			<p class="mb-8 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				When your Planning Center setup works <strong>for</strong> you—not against you—you can spend
				less time chasing details and more time connecting with people. With a clear, optimized system
				in place, your team knows exactly what to do, and you're free to focus on what matters most.
			</p>

			<ul class="mb-10 space-y-4 text-left text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				<li>✓ Finally understand what your system is doing—and what it's missing</li>
				<li>✓ Feel confident handing off tasks and workflows to your team</li>
				<li>✓ Stop worrying about things slipping through the cracks</li>
				<li>✓ Get back to what you were called to do: people, not process</li>
				<li>✓ A calm, clear system that grows with your church</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="text-base text-[#333333] italic sm:text-lg">
				You're just one session away from a smoother, more focused ministry.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-[#F5F5F5] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
				Get clarity. Save time. Serve better.
			</h2>
			<p class="mb-6 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				You don’t have to figure it all out alone. Let’s fix what’s not working and build a system
				that actually supports your ministry.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-8 text-sm text-[#333333] italic sm:text-base">
				This one call could save you hours every week and help your team feel less overwhelmed. Your
				future self will thank you.
			</p>

			<Calendly />

			<p class="mt-6 text-sm text-[#333333] sm:text-base">
				<span class="font-semibold">Need help implementing the fixes?</span><br />
				Your Health Check fee rolls straight into your first Deployment Project—no extra cost to get
				started.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ Section -->
	<section class="bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
			<h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
				Frequently Asked Questions
			</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">How much does the Health Check cost?</h3>
					<p class="text-[#333333]">
						The Health Check is $300. It includes a 60-minute Zoom session, a personalized report, a
						Loom walkthrough, and 7 days of email follow-up.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">
						Do I need to prepare anything before the call?
					</h3>
					<p class="text-[#333333]">
						Just fill out a quick intake form and give manager access to Planning Center—we’ll take
						it from there.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">Will you fix everything for me?</h3>
					<p class="text-[#333333]">
						During the call, we’ll focus on quick wins and diagnosing what needs work. If you want
						hands-on help, your Health Check fee rolls into your first Deployment Project.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">
						Is this for churches that are brand new to Planning Center?
					</h3>
					<p class="text-[#333333]">
						Yes! Whether you're brand new or feeling overwhelmed mid-setup, this Health Check is
						designed to bring clarity and direction.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">What if I’m not technical at all?</h3>
					<p class="text-[#333333]">
						No problem. You don’t need to be a tech expert—I’ll explain everything clearly and make
						sure you leave with a simple plan.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Recap Section -->
	<section class="bg-[#A8C686] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D3557] sm:text-3xl">
				Ready to take control of your Planning Center?
			</h2>
			<p class="mb-6 text-base text-[#333333] sm:text-lg">
				A clearer system, less stress, and more time for the ministry that matters most are just one
				call away. Let’s uncover exactly what’s not working and fix it together—so you can get back
				to serving your church.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-8 text-sm text-[#333333] italic sm:text-base">
				Your Health Check fee goes toward your first Deployment Project, so you can get the help you
				need—without the extra cost.
			</p>

			<Calendly />
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Footer Section -->
	<section class="mt-12 text-center text-[#333333]">
		<p>
			Questions?<br /> Email me ➡️ <a
				href="mailto:nolan@sundayreadysolutions.com"
				class="font-semibold text-[#1D3557]">nolan@sundayreadysolutions.com</a
			>
		</p>
	</section>
</Layout>
